                  "name": "Content Frame",
                  "width": 600,
                  "layout": "vertical",
                  "gap": 28,
                  "children": [
                    {
                      "type": "frame",
                      "id": "lJoDz",
                      "name": "Title Block",
                      "width": "fill_container",
                      "layout": "vertical",
                      "gap": 8,
                      "children": [
                        {
                          "type": "text",
                          "id": "jDWC6",
                          "name": "titleText",
                          "fill": "#141414",
                          "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                          "width": "fill_container",
                          "content": "The Morning After",
                          "fontFamily": "EB Garamond",
                          "fontSize": 38
                        },
                        {
                          "type": "text",
                          "id": "UI5GF",
                          "name": "metaText",
                          "fill": "#A3A3A3",
                          "content": "POV: Maren · Timeline: 2062",
                          "fontFamily": "Inter",
                          "fontSize": 11,
                          "fontWeight": "normal"
                        }
                      ]
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "id": "DMjiH",
                      "name": "scene1Label",
                      "fill": "#C4C4C4",
                      "content": "Kitchen morning",
                      "fontFamily": "Inter",
                      "fontSize": 10,
                      "fontWeight": "normal",
                      "letterSpacing": 0.04
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "id": "ZbETW",
                      "name": "para1",
                      "fill": "#2E2E2E",
                      "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                      "width": "fill_container",
                      "content": "The coffee machine hissed its familiar morning protest, steam curling upward in lazy spirals that caught the thin light filtering through the kitchen blinds. Maren stood with her back against the counter, arms crossed, watching the display cycle through its startup sequence. Outside, the city hummed with the quiet efficiency of six AM — delivery drones threading between buildings, the distant whisper of maglev trains.",
                      "lineHeight": 1.67,
                      "fontFamily": "EB Garamond",
                      "fontSize": 18,
                      "fontWeight": "normal"
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "id": "l6QCQ",
                      "name": "para2",
                      "fill": "#2E2E2E",
                      "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                      "width": "fill_container",
                      "content": "She picked up the mug before the machine had finished, letting the last drops splash against porcelain. The apartment was still — Jonas wouldn't be up for another hour, and the silence felt like something she could hold in her hands, fragile and temporary.",
                      "lineHeight": 1.67,
                      "fontFamily": "EB Garamond",
                      "fontSize": 18,
                      "fontWeight": "normal"
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "id": "UL36t",
                      "name": "scene2Label",
                      "fill": "#C4C4C4",
                      "content": "Jonas arrives",
                      "fontFamily": "Inter",
                      "fontSize": 10,
                      "fontWeight": "normal",
                      "letterSpacing": 0.04
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "id": "LpFmG",
                      "name": "para3",
                      "fill": "#2E2E2E",
                      "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                      "width": "fill_container",
                      "content": "The sound of bare feet on hardwood preceded him — that particular shuffle Jonas had when he was still half-asleep, navigating more by memory than sight. He appeared in the doorway, hair compressed on one side, squinting against even the modest kitchen light.",
                      "lineHeight": 1.67,
                      "fontFamily": "EB Garamond",
                      "fontSize": 18,
                      "fontWeight": "normal"
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "id": "gyzVY",
                      "name": "para4",
                      "fill": "#2E2E2E",
                      "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                      "width": "fill_container",
                      "content": "'You're up early.' His voice carried the gravel of sleep, but his eyes were already tracking to the coffee machine, calculating whether she'd left him any.",
                      "lineHeight": 1.67,
                      "fontFamily": "EB Garamond",
                      "fontSize": 18,
                      "fontWeight": "normal"
                    }
                  ]
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
